text: The 2020 United States presidential election in West Virginia was held on Tuesday, November 3, 2020, as part of the 2020 United States presidential election. Incumbent President Donald Trumpand running mate Vice President Mike Pence had won 5 electoral votes in the Electoral College. == References == Category:2020 United States presidential election Category:21st century in West Virginia
title: 2020 United States presidential election in West Virginia
